      !-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      !  Subroutine   :                   ppm_io_close
      !-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      !
      !  Purpose      : This routine closes an IO channel.
      !
      !  Input        : iUnit          (I) IO unit to be closed.
      !
      !  Input/output :
      !
      !  Output       : info           (I) return code. 0 on success.
      !
      !  Remarks      : 
      !
      !  References   :
      !
      !  Revisions    :
